Class ArrayNetClass

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NetObject

    public class ArrayNetClass
extends NetClass
    NetClass implementation that uses an ArrayList as a back-end. This class is better than HashNetClass for containing a small number of NetObject instances.
    Since:
    1.0
